  <brief_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Sequential Ascending, Single-dose Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics, and Pharmacodynamics of E2212 in Healthy Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Sequential Ascending, Single-dose Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics, and Pharmacodynamics of E2212 in Healthy Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
